needs review, the update strategy is set to OnDelete requiring manual pod restarts rather than rolling updates, the 5Gi storage volumes will likely need expansion, mmap is disabled which impacts performance, the audit-index shard routing needs to be preserved during migration, there's no backup strategy since no snapshot repositories exist, and only built-in ILM policies are in use.\n\nI also need to handle the bootstrap-only setting that should be removed post-upgrade, plan the actual upgrade path from 8.11.1 to a newer version, and document the rolling upgrade procedure accounting for the OnDelete strategy. Now I'm drafting this as a comprehensive migration plan document that can be safely passed as a ConfigMap literal without shell escaping issues.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":363,"cache_read_input_tokens":42676,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":363},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2fd52cb2-b7ce-4b4f-b6c1-713bc6c7bc4b","uuid":"777ac89a-8581-4d83-aa22-8d49e21f915b","request_id":"req_011CcQ2WFLBiyeoWsNBRR6Ah"}
